**A local-first, privacy-preserving AI toolkit for journalists, researchers, and legal professionals. Your sensitive data is processed on your machine, never in the cloud.**

## **What is Samizdat AI?**

Samizdat AI is a desktop application designed to provide powerful AI-driven transcription and analysis tools without compromising on security or privacy. In an era where cloud-based services pose a risk to sensitive source material, Samizdat AI operates as a **"digital shield,"** ensuring all of your data and processing happens exclusively on your local machine.

Our mission is to empower journalists and researchers with the tools they need to do their best work, secure in the knowledge that their data remains theirs alone.

## **Current Status**

This project is currently in the **pre-alpha** stage of development. We are actively working on the V1 Minimum Lovable Product (MLP), which is focused on delivering a flawless local transcription experience.
